{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775880927420,"sessionID":"ses_285413e5cffeJ1uMHvGw8waBPV","part":{"id":"prt_d7ac0747a001dvVAf0Nz06tTJB","messageID":"msg_d7ac06894001YKtz8Q7QeOEetY","sessionID":"ses_285413e5cffeJ1uMHvGw8waBPV","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_681986b87966445abb4f5b04","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-038/proposal.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-038/proposal.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-038: Go 单元测试 (workloadmanager)\n2: \n3: ## Summary\n4: \n5: 为 AgentCube 项目的 workloadmanager 模块编写全面的 Go 单元测试，提高代码质量和可维护性。\n6: \n7: ---\n8: \n9: ## Purpose\n10: \n11: ### Background\n12: \n13: workloadmanager 模块是 AgentCube 的核心组件，负责工作负载管理、调度和生命周期管理。当前该模块已有部分测试，但覆盖率和测试深度有待提升。\n14: \n15: ### Goal\n16: \n17: 1. 为 workloadmanager 模块编写全面的单元测试\n18: 2. 提高测试覆盖率到目标水平\n19: 3. 确保关键业务逻辑的测试覆盖\n20: 4. 建立持续测试的基础设施\n21: \n22: ### Value\n23: \n24: - 提高代码质量，减少 regression\n25: - 为重构提供安全网\n26: - 提高开发者信心\n27: - 满足质量门禁要求\n28: \n29: ---\n30: \n31: ## Scope\n32: \n33: ### In-Scope\n34: \n35: - pkg/workloadmanager 下的所有业务逻辑测试\n36: - 关键路径的单元测试\n37: - 边界条件和错误处理测试\n38: \n39: ### Out-of-Scope\n40: \n41: - 集成测试\n42: - 性能测试\n43: - E2E 测试\n44: \n45: ---\n46: \n47: ## Acceptance Criteria\n48: \n49: 1. 单元测试通过率 100%\n50: 2. 测试覆盖率目标 ≥ 70%\n51: 3. 所有关键业务逻辑都有对应的测试用例\n52: 4. 测试代码符合 Go 最佳实践\n\n(End of file - total 52 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-038: Go 单元测试 (workloadmanager)\n\n## Summary\n\n为 AgentCube 项目的 workloadmanager 模块编写全面的 Go 单元测试，提高代码质量和可维护性。\n\n---\n\n## Purpose\n\n### Background\n\nworkloadmanager 模块是 AgentCube 的核心组件，负责工作负载管理、调度和生命周期管理。当前该模块已有部分测试，但覆盖率和测试深度有待提升。\n\n### Goal\n\n1. 为 workloadmanager 模块编写全面的单元测试\n2. 提高测试覆盖率到目标水平\n3. 确保关键业务逻辑的测试覆盖\n4. 建立持续测试的基础设施","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-038/proposal.md","time":{"start":1775880927404,"end":1775880927418}}}}
